{"tid":1093811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵會展站再有 6 沉降點獲政府放寬標準","createTime":"2019-04-05T22:50:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-05T23:33:48.000Z","uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"662dcf5205a00c70e3f34ec1857aac1745e77c4c","tid":1093811,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T22:50:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/a_SYAVU_1200x0.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fa_SYAVU_1200x0.PNG&h=bd7a67af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵會展站一度因沉降超標停工，去年 9 月會展站附近 121 沉降監測點獲政府放寬停工指標而復工。港鐵向灣仔區議會提交文件，預計沙中綫紅磡至金鐘段，及會展站的完工日期，維持以2021年通車為目標，會展站的大型挖掘工程亦預計在今年上半年完成。港鐵指出，獲政府放寬監測標準之後，沉降監測點數據再出現超標的情況。另外，港鐵獲當局放寬 6 個監測點的預設停工指標。<br />\n<br />\n文件提到，自去年10月後，港鐵再獲港府同意放寬6個監測點的預設暫時停工指標，當局放寬 6 個監測點的預設停工指標，其中在會展站及西面連接隧道，3個水管監測點的沉降幅度分別錄得3.7、7.8及8.4毫米；惟更新後的沉降上限是90、70和50毫米，未有超標。<br />\n<br />\n文件提到，會展站西面至金鐘站之連接隧道，3 個路面監測點由於在完成重鋪路後，工程人員重新設定沉降監測點數據為零，新的沉降上限是25毫米。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵指出，工程團隊會繼續謹慎進行工程，亦會繼續密切監察附近建築物及地下管綫狀況。若沉降監測數據達至工程設定指標，會採取跟進措施。<br />\n<br />\n沙中綫會展站工地附近設置的監測點，鑑於部分沉降幅度超出預設停工指標，港鐵去年8月暫停挖掘工程。至9月，政府把會展站及西面連接隧道121處監測點的停工指標更新，百多個已經出現沉降的監測點，均受惠於放寬停工指標，當中有路面已沉降75.4毫米，但卻獲准放寬至沉降90毫米才需停工。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E6%9C%83%E5%B1%95%E7%AB%99%E5%86%8D%E6%9C%89-6-%E6%B2%89%E9%99%8D%E9%BB%9E%E7%8D%B2%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%94%BE%E5%AF%AC%E6%A8%99%E6%BA%96/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25B1%2595%25E7%25AB%2599%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%259C%2589-6-%25E6%25B2%2589%25E9%2599%258D%25E9%25BB%259E%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%2594%25BE%25E5%25AF%25AC%25E6%25A8%2599%25E6%25BA%2596%2F&d=K4UaoR%2Bzp7qM8XPwf0LBI3s01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=26d9e163\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25B1%2595%25E7%25AB%2599%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%259C%2589-6-%25E6%25B2%2589%25E9%2599%258D%25E9%25BB%259E%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%2594%25BE%25E5%25AF%25AC%25E6%25A8%2599%25E6%25BA%2596%2F&h=adb91100\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E6%9C%83%E5%B1%95%E7%AB%99%E5%86%8D%E6%9C%89-6-%E6%B2%89%E9%99%8D%E9%BB%9E%E7%8D%B2%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%94%BE%E5%AF%AC%E6%A8%99%E6%BA%96/</a>"},{"pid":"febb3d53a83da01de2b1b90c9ed3405d5b2eaddf","tid":1093811,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T23:08:23.000Z","msg":"隻龜就落到海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed69109bb2921530c99dcb415b4deff764d5e37","tid":1093811,"uid":769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T23:21:41.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"ca0db259b5d344c3b12e0d5e248d53fbfa1e071d","tid":1093811,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"febb3d53a83da01de2b1b90c9ed3405d5b2eaddf","tid":1093811,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T23:08:23.000Z","msg":"隻龜就落到海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T23:23:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb9d780323ea434e0266fc2dc294f2ed640ae56f","tid":1093811,"uid":126283,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T23:27:20.000Z","msg":"不如廢左套標準啦，反正都唔洗跟"},{"pid":"852f538bb8311fcb0081aea7ae51a89e9210059c","tid":1093811,"uid":30794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T23:29:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cbe825fa138830eaf2bbccd76e270d08150e06f","tid":1093811,"uid":61545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb9d780323ea434e0266fc2dc294f2ed640ae56f","tid":1093811,"uid":126283,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"repl